{"tid":770099,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【李華華搶先睇】嘉道理26歲細仔入中電董事局","createTime":"2018-08-06T17:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T01:20:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31f2290f7f746aea8149a2213df7a99b5aeb91e6","tid":770099,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T17:49:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180806/58531823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58531823&d=E5UWrIDhKMu6tZp4Qm1do5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3c9a7f22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58531823&h=919d9429\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180806/58531823</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180806/large/1533563227_2837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180806%2Flarge%2F1533563227_2837.jpg&h=24f5ad32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPhilip Lawrence Kadoorie中文名「可飛利」都幾特別<br />\n<br />\n中電(002)出咗份靚仔業績，同時宣佈委任年僅26歲嘅Philip Lawrence Kadoorie（可飛利）做非執董，一睇姓氏，就知道呢位哥仔係中電主席米高嘉道理個仔喇。<br />\n<br />\n77歲嘅嘉道理有三名子女，今次細仔入局，似係鋪定慢慢長路，畀細仔熟知集團運作，佢本人就唔似想退休，事關佢舊年講過，爸爸Lawrence Kadoorie去世前一日仍照常上班，只要健康，佢都會繼續返工。<br />\n<br />\n睇番公司通告，Philip波士頓大學傳理系畢業，持有直升機商用飛行員執照，舊年又喺北京清華完成高級普通話課程。佢之前喺中電同施羅德實習過。同時，佢係嘉道理父子有限公司董事，負責監管家族多項權益，接班人非佢莫屬，時間問題啫。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，佢舊年已經被委任為集團同系上市公司大酒店(045)嘅非執董。<br />\n<br />\n中電同時委任渣打香港前一姐陳秀梅（May Tan）做獨立非執董。兩位新董事，每年分別有55萬袍金，除開每月4.6萬，以非執董而言算係唔錯。陳秀梅坐埋另外幾個公司內部委員會，仲有額外酬金㖭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中電今日股價創新高見90蚊，又邀得猛人入局，真係可喜可賀。"},{"pid":"c1c6b25f072ccf1c23115a1a4bebb4e01f141d50","tid":770099,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"36歲"},{"pid":"b4f899b9a54d34f1e57c6d44d8b1a6eb34d4b9e8","tid":770099,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"26定36⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果26的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就黎26歲既我究竟係到做緊咩"},{"pid":"82e4dab32272776c6bcbde5d053988c8c0bbe9ba","tid":770099,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f899b9a54d34f1e57c6d44d8b1a6eb34d4b9e8","tid":770099,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"26定36⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果26的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就黎26歲既我究竟係到做緊咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"打j同打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a9e568a9f88ba870c4e3c74bba1f1b3d9531bf","tid":770099,"uid":132081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"之後佢又會教你做人要努力就可以入去中電董事局做"},{"pid":"cfc90ca62ca28c4dbdfe55f9ba9a40da11e8cf33","tid":770099,"uid":41356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"張相影得咁自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e196277307c832f48aa0e23751b57c3028fd218","tid":770099,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:17:00.000Z","msg":"成功需父幹"},{"pid":"9c66dcb0a0930b32dec81a3d8a4ded55969b9cb9","tid":770099,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"以為係靚仔洋腸先上到報，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}